ame strategy to other countries, such as Mexico, in the present or future.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aCounterinsurgency -- Colombia. 0aCounterinsurgencyzColombia. 0aDrug control -- Colombia. 0aDrug controlzColombia. 0aEconomic assistance, AmericanzColombia. 0aInsurgency -- Colombia. 0aInsurgencyzColombia. 0aMilitary assistance, AmericanzColombia. 0aNational security -- Colombia. 0aNational securityzColombia. 4aHistory : History. 4aLatin American, Caribbean, and Latinx Studies : Latin American Studies. 4aPolitics and Law : Conflict Resolution. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Science. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / International Relations / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143845300240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438453002423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438453002/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles